Third-Party Data Sources
========================
This knowledge graph incorporates data derived from:

- IOM Dietary Reference Intakes (Public Domain)
  National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine
  https://www.nationalacademies.org

- FDA Daily Values (Public Domain)
  U.S. Food and Drug Administration
  https://www.fda.gov

- WHO/FAO Nutrient Requirements (CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO)
  World Health Organization / Food and Agriculture Organization
  https://www.who.int

- University of Sydney Glycemic Index Database
  https://www.glycemicindex.com

Please cite original sources when using derived data in publications.
See CITATION.cff for recommended citation format.
